Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.30,0:00:42.64,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Can't sleep, Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.27,0:00:45.02,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I just came to check on you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.39,0:00:46.44,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Go back to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.94,0:00:48.36,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,'Kay.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.19,0:00:52.11,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Good night, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.11,0:00:54.07,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,See you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.40,0:00:56.45,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, night.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.22,0:01:24.31,sign_3370_33_The_Rising_of_th,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(750,645)}The Rising of the Shield Hero
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.88,0:02:41.18,sign_3738_9_Curse_Shield,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(486,682)}Curse Shield
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.39,0:02:48.89,main,W,0000,0000,0000,,You folks had better turn back.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.39,0:02:51.60,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,If you keep going, you'll die.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.35,0:02:55.15,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,We heard there's a village down this path.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.03,0:02:57.86,main,W,0000,0000,0000,,The village is done for.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.49,0:03:02.07,main,W,0000,0000,0000,,The plague even got the village elder.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.04,0:03:07.66,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,What could be happening there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.16,0:03:09.58,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,We'll see when we get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.26,0:03:27.43,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,What brings you to a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.43,0:03:29.89,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a traveling merchant.\N I'm here to sell you medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.89,0:03:31.64,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,A traveling merchant?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.64,0:03:33.81,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, that filolial...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.15,0:03:36.02,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be the Heavenly Fowl?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.32,0:03:38.19,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.82,0:03:41.53,main,D,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.53,0:03:45.91,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Our Savior of the Heavenly \NFowl has come for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.20,0:03:48.58,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,"Doctor"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.58,0:03:51.33,main,D,0000,0000,0000,,I run the village clinic.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.33,0:03:54.42,main,D,0000,0000,0000,,If I may ask, are you really...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.83,0:03:56.84,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I'm only here to sell you medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.84,0:03:58.71,main,D,0000,0000,0000,,Even that would be a great help!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.71,0:04:01.80,main,D,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot make nearly enough for everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.64,0:04:08.89,main,Nur,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor, who are these people?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.89,0:04:12.02,main,D,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, they say they'll sell us medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.02,0:04:15.02,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Looking at this, I should probably \Ngive it to them myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.62,0:04:33.54,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.14,0:04:47.93,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Fifty silvers, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.93,0:04:49.81,main,D,0000,0000,0000,,Will it do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.81,0:04:52.81,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,You're a bit short, but I'll take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.81,0:04:55.94,main,D,0000,0000,0000,,You were truly a great help.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.94,0:04:57.81,main,D,0000,0000,0000,,Now we've staved off the immediate crisis.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.81,0:04:58.69,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Are you satisfied with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.15,0:05:03.40,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,All I did was treat their symptoms.\N I didn't cure them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.40,0:05:05.32,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,They'll eventually go back to square one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.32,0:05:07.91,main,D,0000,0000,0000,,You're indeed right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.91,0:05:10.91,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Not that I mind, since I'll \Nmake good money anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.91,0:05:15.79,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see what dies out first,\N you or your coffers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.79,0:05:18.25,main,Nur,0000,0000,0000,,We know that we can't let this go on!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.25,0:05:18.96,main,Nur,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.96,0:05:21.00,main,Nur,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.42,0:05:22.96,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.38,0:05:29.18,main,Nur,0000,0000,0000,,We believe the wind from the mountain \Nthat's home to monsters is the cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.55,0:05:31.47,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,The mountain that's home to monsters?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.47,0:05:35.93,main,D,0000,0000,0000,,Around a month ago, a large \Ndragon that nested there
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.93,0:05:39.40,main,D,0000,0000,0000,,was killed by the Sword Hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.40,0:05:41.90,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I did hear rumors about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.36,0:05:45.15,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,But what does that have \Nto do with the plague?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.49,0:05:48.78,main,D,0000,0000,0000,,In order to see the dragon's \Ncorpse and gather materials,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.78,0:05:51.41,main,D,0000,0000,0000,,many adventurers came to our village.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.41,0:05:55.00,main,D,0000,0000,0000,,That certainly did help \Nthe village flourish.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.41,0:05:58.87,main,D,0000,0000,0000,,But one day, an adventurer collapsed, and more followed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.87,0:06:04.30,main,D,0000,0000,0000,,The dragon's flesh must have begun \Nto rot and emit some kind of poison.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.63,0:06:06.01,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,Damn Ren.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.01,0:06:10.59,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,Even a high schooler like him should \Nknow that meat rots when you leave it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.14,0:06:16.43,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I guess it must've slipped his mind,\N since he thinks this world is a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.43,0:06:20.31,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,If you know the cause, \Nthen why don't you get rid of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.31,0:06:25.44,main,Nur,0000,0000,0000,,That mountain's filled with violent monsters,\N so only adventurers can go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.44,0:06:27.03,main,Nur,0000,0000,0000,,We can't do anything about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.03,0:06:32.49,main,D,0000,0000,0000,,And perhaps due to the dragon's poison, \Nthe ecology there has changed, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.91,0:06:37.62,main,D,0000,0000,0000,,The average adventurer cannot \Nget anywhere near the corpse.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.08,0:06:39.87,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Have you informed the\N royal court about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.87,0:06:43.50,main,D,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. We're slated to receive \Na medicine delivery shortly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.50,0:06:48.01,main,Nur,0000,0000,0000,,But they said the heroes are \Ntoo busy to help for a while yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.34,0:06:49.76,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.76,0:06:52.09,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Cancel the request you made to the court.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.85,0:06:53.85,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Raphtalia...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.26,0:06:55.60,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare to set out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.60,0:06:56.52,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.52,0:06:59.56,main,D,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, are you planning to go yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.56,0:07:01.31,main,D,0000,0000,0000,,It's too dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.31,0:07:04.40,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. We're used to danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.40,0:07:07.61,main,D,0000,0000,0000,,I can't find the words to \Nexpress our gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.61,0:07:09.24,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Keep your thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.24,0:07:10.82,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,What I want is money.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.82,0:07:12.49,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Five hundred silvers will cover it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.49,0:07:15.33,main,D,0000,0000,0000,,Five hundred? That's too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.33,0:07:17.12,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,That includes hazard pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.12,0:07:20.37,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,You can just pay me what you \Nwere going to pay the court.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.37,0:07:22.88,main,Nur,0000,0000,0000,,"Savior," my foot. \NHe's just a money-grubber.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.88,0:07:24.38,main,D,0000,0000,0000,,Stop that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.71,0:07:27.59,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I don't recall ever calling myself a savior.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.01,0:07:35.30,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,You're deliberately trying to make them hate you, \Naren't you, Naofumi-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.30,0:07:37.64,sign_16043_89_Chimera_Viper_Sh,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Chimera Viper Shield — Poison Resistance (Med)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.02,0:07:42.35,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I know we're dealing \Nwith a dragon here,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.73,0:07:44.73,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,but this is a huge loadout.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.73,0:07:46.69,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,We had to take the wagon either way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.69,0:07:48.82,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,A little more luggage is no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.23,0:07:53.28,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,We could've traveled lighter if \NFilo hadn't thrown a tantrum.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.66,0:07:56.78,flashback,F,0000,0000,0000,,I've made a lifetime's worth\N of memories with this wagon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.78,0:07:58.45,flashback,F,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna leave it behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.45,0:08:01.29,flashback,N,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, your lifetime of one whole month.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.96,0:08:05.58,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what to do \Nabout Filo's selfishness.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.58,0:08:09.51,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, it might've \Nbeen a pretty good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.88,0:08:14.34,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,We'll never get anywhere \Nif we try to fight them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.97,0:08:17.72,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,As Shield Hero, source of \Nthy power, I order thee.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.72,0:08:20.68,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Decipher the laws of nature \Nand defend my target.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.35,0:08:22.60,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Fast Guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.06,0:08:25.48,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Run right through them, Filo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.48,0:08:26.90,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,'Kay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.74,0:08:38.28,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,The air here is stagnant.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.28,0:08:40.16,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Stay back if you're having a hard time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.16,0:08:42.41,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.41,0:08:43.37,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.66,0:08:47.17,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,But man, we should've \Neaten before coming here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.67,0:08:50.34,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Looking at this is making \Nme lose my appetite.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.17,0:08:54.51,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Looking at it made me hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.30,0:08:56.76,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Don't overeat!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.80,0:09:02.35,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Looking at its size, even taking \Nit apart will be a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.53,0:09:23.33,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,A dragon zombie?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.04,0:09:26.08,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,What do we do, Naofumi-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.79,0:09:28.29,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,For now, get away from it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.05,0:09:35.42,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,A dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.42,0:09:36.68,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,I hate dragons!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.85,0:09:42.60,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we {\i1}can{\i0} fight it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.98,0:09:48.73,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Get behind me, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.45,0:09:59.03,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,My shield can't block all\N of its poison breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.03,0:10:01.08,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,I have resistance, but Raphtalia doesn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.62,0:10:02.53,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,Still...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.99,0:10:06.71,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't stop it here, \Nit'll cause even more problems!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.00,0:10:09.71,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Now I'm mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.33,0:10:12.00,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Filo! Don't fight it alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.01,0:10:18.97,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,We have to get away and regroup.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.97,0:10:20.59,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Raphtalia.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.59,0:10:21.64,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Filo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.60,0:10:23.68,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,That idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.01,0:10:24.85,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.85,0:10:25.72,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Filo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.23,0:10:37.24,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Filo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.13,0:10:58.13,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,Again?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.05,0:11:00.97,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,Am I going to lose it all again?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.14,0:11:06.77,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,Is this world going to take \Neverything from me again?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.56,0:11:09.14,sign_22406_138_d0_Y0u_s33k_PoWe,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,d0 Y0u s33k PoWeR?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.73,0:11:10.85,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,Power?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.85,0:11:14.06,sign_22406_138_d0_Y0u_s33k_PoWe,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,D0 yOU haT3 3veRYtHiNG?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.23,0:11:15.32,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,Hate?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.82,0:11:17.61,sign_22406_138_d0_Y0u_s33k_PoWe,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,D0 yOU haT3 3veRYtHiNG?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.61,0:11:19.65,sign_22708_143_Curse_Series____,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(191,210)}Curse Series — Rage Shield
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.58,0:11:26.66,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,I hate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.29,0:11:29.37,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,I hate it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.54,0:11:35.46,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,Hate...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.93,0:11:45.97,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,Hate!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.98,0:11:57.07,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you kill Filo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.36,0:12:00.36,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,No, Naofumi-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.46,0:12:13.29,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Naofumi-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.38,0:12:20.80,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.80,0:12:22.55,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Not Naofumi-sama, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.78,0:12:43.28,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Naofumi-sama?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.85,0:13:14.18,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Burn.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.53,0:13:27.32,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,Kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.07,0:13:31.16,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,Kill them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.16,0:13:43.92,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,Suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.22,0:13:52.64,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.81,0:13:55.39,flashback,R,0000,0000,0000,,I believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.27,0:14:00.40,flashback,R,0000,0000,0000,,I am your sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.90,0:14:03.19,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,This voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.19,0:14:08.07,flashback,R,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you can't trust \Nanyone anymore, I trust you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.61,0:14:12.21,flashback,R,0000,0000,0000,,I trust the great Shield Hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.95,0:14:15.41,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,What was I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.00,0:14:18.04,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Naofumi-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.21,0:14:22.13,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness... you're back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.96,0:14:26.00,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Raphtalia!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.42,0:14:27.68,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,What's all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.97,0:14:29.89,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.35,0:14:35.22,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,As Shield Hero, source of \Nthy power, I order thee.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.22,0:14:38.17,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Decipher the laws of nature \Nand heal my target.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.64,0:14:39.94,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Fast Heal!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.40,0:14:45.03,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Heal my target!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.03,0:14:46.44,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Fast Heal!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.03,0:14:50.03,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I said heal, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.03,0:14:51.94,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Fast Heal!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.62,0:14:53.95,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,It's my fault...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.37,0:14:57.33,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.21,0:15:02.25,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.88,0:15:06.42,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,To defeat the dragon,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.84,0:15:08.97,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,I have to use this power.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.97,0:15:09.88,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.51,0:15:13.22,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,If I lose focus, hatred will consume my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.30,0:15:15.60,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,What can I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.37,0:15:38.50,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,What just happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.50,0:15:40.08,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Naofumi-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.08,0:15:42.33,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Raphtalia!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.67,0:15:43.58,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.29,0:15:49.13,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... thanks to your healing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.67,0:15:53.05,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to the dragon?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.36,0:16:09.94,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Is that you, Filo?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.90,0:16:13.53,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,I finally got back out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.53,0:16:14.70,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,You're okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.70,0:16:15.53,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.03,0:16:18.79,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,But you were eaten,\N and there was all that blood...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.79,0:16:20.12,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.12,0:16:24.50,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I threw up my food when I got gobbled.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.04,0:16:28.92,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,It was that red fruit?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.25,0:16:33.18,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Were you worried about me, Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.05,0:16:35.05,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.47,0:16:38.01,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you looking away?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.01,0:16:39.31,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Get away from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.31,0:16:42.73,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,So, wait, you killed the dragon, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.02,0:16:47.44,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Yep. When I was tearing at its \Nbelly trying to get out,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.44,0:16:50.73,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,I found a big purple crystal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.73,0:16:52.19,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,It was shining.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.19,0:16:53.45,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,A crystal?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.15,0:16:56.74,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,That was its core, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.24,0:16:58.87,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,So, where's the crystal?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.25,0:17:04.37,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,You ate it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.63,0:17:07.71,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Raphtalia!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.29,0:17:09.25,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.71,0:17:13.34,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,We'll give her the medicine in the carriage \Nand head back to the village at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.34,0:17:14.51,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.01,0:17:17.30,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,We have to deal with the dragon's corpse.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.30,0:17:18.89,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,You come first!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.35,0:17:21.27,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.27,0:17:24.35,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take that medicine \Nand lie down for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.23,0:17:27.77,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Filo, let's hurry and clean this mess up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.77,0:17:28.94,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,'Kay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.90,0:17:33.07,main,D,0000,0000,0000,,The mountain wind has gone back to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.07,0:17:34.57,main,D,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be all right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.28,0:17:37.95,main,D,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.95,0:17:40.33,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Use that money to treat Raphtalia.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.70,0:17:42.33,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care how much it costs.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.33,0:17:43.79,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Please cure her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.58,0:17:47.37,main,D,0000,0000,0000,,Curing her will be difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.37,0:17:51.25,main,D,0000,0000,0000,,She's been afflicted with a curse, \Nand a powerful one at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.71,0:17:55.51,main,D,0000,0000,0000,,We've wrapped her with bandages \Nsoaked in holy water,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.84,0:18:00.72,main,D,0000,0000,0000,,but we don't have holy water \Npure enough to dispel curses.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.01,0:18:04.56,main,D,0000,0000,0000,,If you go to a church in a big town,\N I'm sure you'll find some.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.56,0:18:07.90,main,D,0000,0000,0000,,Keep this money for when you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.81,0:18:09.98,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.11,0:18:15.61,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.61,0:18:17.82,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I've been tended to,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.82,0:18:19.24,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,so I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.24,0:18:22.53,main,Nur,0000,0000,0000,,I never knew corpses could inflict \Nsuch powerful curses.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.45,0:18:25.79,main,Nur,0000,0000,0000,,Dragons are terrifying creatures.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.50,0:18:27.33,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.75,0:18:31.25,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't have been so careless and \Ngotten all that rotten flesh on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.51,0:18:37.68,main,Nur,0000,0000,0000,,He cares about you very much, doesn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.68,0:18:39.55,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Er, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.84,0:18:42.35,main,Nur,0000,0000,0000,,Take care, Raphtalia-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.81,0:18:46.06,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.73,0:18:48.23,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.77,0:18:50.06,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,It's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.06,0:18:55.07,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I got the feeling that power would \Ntake you somewhere far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.86,0:19:01.66,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,So, given that I was able to stop you,\N this doesn't bother me one bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.87,0:19:07.04,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Are you leaving us, Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.04,0:19:08.54,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.67,0:19:12.75,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,I have a gift for you, Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.04,0:19:15.25,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.13,0:19:19.76,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,A crystal that was inside the dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.76,0:19:21.72,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,You threw it up?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.47,0:19:25.81,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,No! I kept this one to be a gift!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.68,0:19:31.81,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,If this is a crystallization of the \Nresidual mana from the dragon's corpse...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.78,0:19:40.65,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,My level isn't high enough, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.24,0:19:44.58,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,That shield wasn't in the upgrade tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.16,0:19:47.49,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,If I'd continued to use its power,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.83,0:19:51.92,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,I would've killed both Raphtalia and Filo,\N who was inside the dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.88,0:19:54.46,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Naofumi-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.34,0:19:57.46,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.30,0:20:03.09,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I put you both in danger \Nbecause I hesitated.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.76,0:20:08.10,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Just as bravery and recklessness differ,\N so too do caution and cowardice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.64,0:20:11.81,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,If I remain a coward, I'll fail \Nto protect the things I care about.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.52,0:20:17.32,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Back then, I should've stepped \Nup and distracted the dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.73,0:20:19.65,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,There were so many things I could've done.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.03,0:20:22.53,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't your fault, Naofumi-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.53,0:20:25.28,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,If only I had been stronger...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.28,0:20:26.91,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,I messed up, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.91,0:20:29.54,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,I charged in because \NI hate dragons so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.20,0:20:31.62,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,You two...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.34,0:20:40.46,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,We are stronger now than we were yesterday,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.46,0:20:42.22,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,and we'll be even stronger tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.09,0:20:45.18,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Let's keep that up, one day at a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.47,0:20:46.89,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, let's. Together.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.30,0:20:48.56,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,I'll work hard, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.72,0:20:50.39,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.93,0:20:52.98,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, you smiled, Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.14,0:20:55.69,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.69,0:20:58.44,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,You finally showed us a normal smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.44,0:21:00.15,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Did I...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.15,0:21:02.70,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Yep! Right, Onee-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.70,0:21:03.49,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.16,0:21:07.74,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,It's gotten late.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.74,0:21:09.87,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Get some sleep and rest up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.87,0:21:11.29,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,'Kay!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.87,0:21:13.46,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.67,0:21:18.13,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Could you spend the night with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.71,0:21:19.88,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Don't want to be lonely?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.88,0:21:21.59,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.59,0:21:24.47,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I would be allowed \Nto have this, just this once.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.47,0:21:25.36,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Filo...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.16,0:21:28.58,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Sleep with Raphtalia tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.58,0:21:29.86,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,'Kay!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.86,0:21:30.44,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.44,0:21:31.84,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,You're cold, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.16,0:21:35.39,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I meant...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.97,0:21:38.75,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Join us, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.75,0:21:39.70,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.94,0:21:42.86,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not warm, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.27,0:21:52.65,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,I have to grow stronger...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.74,0:21:57.74,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,Along with the people who believe in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.68,0:22:00.10,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,And I'll protect them,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.99,0:22:03.66,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,come what may!
